Face Recognition Project
This project uses the face_recognition library along with OpenCV to perform face detection and recognition in images or live video from a webcam.

Requirements
Before running the project, ensure that you have the necessary libraries installed. You can install them using the following commands:


pip install face_recognition
pip install opencv-python
Usage
1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/your_username/face_recognition_project.git
cd face_recognition_project
2. Run the Face Recognition Script
For Image:
Replace "your_image.jpg" with the path to the image you want to process.


python face_recognition_script.py "your_image.jpg"
For Webcam (Live Video):


python webcam_face_recognition.py
Press 'q' to exit the live video feed.

Notes
The project uses the face_recognition library for face detection and recognition.
Make sure to have a webcam connected if you are using the live video script.
Feel free to customize the project according to your needs!
